Suggests: libastral0 (>= 0.9.2)
Description: Client for reading LOR, written on versatile Tcl/Tk.
 This is a stupid client for reading LOR, written on versatile Tcl/Tk
 .
 Main features:
 .
 * Message posting
 .
 * Ability to view messages in topic as tree like modern news readers
 .
 * Message caching and offline browsing
 .
 * Personal ignore list
 .
 * Message coloring
 .
 * "Favorites" to keep favorite flames
 .
 * User tagging